牛津布魯克斯大學的建築學，房地產管理, 城市規劃，測量和歷史有較其他學科為高的質量<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/education/1709497.stm|title=Oxford's history blow|publisher=BBC News|date=14 December 2001|accessdate=2014-05-13|archive-date=2009-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090129135252/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/education/1709497.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，實際上建築學院是全英最大的建築學院之一，常列在同類學院中全英前五位<ref>''Architects' Journal'' 4 May 2006 page 84</ref>。
當中醫療學科,包括物理治療，職業治療等亦是全英第五。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/education/ng-interactive/2014/jun/03/university-guide-2015-league-table-for-health-professions|title=University guide 2015: league table for health professions|publisher=卫报|date=3 June 2014|accessdate=2015-05-09|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305114034/http://www.theguardian.com/education/ng-interactive/2014/jun/03/university-guide-2015-league-table-for-health-professions|dead-url=no}}</ref>

